name: Agena
description: A collection of 10,000 unique interactive art beings living on ethereum created by SiA and David OReilly. SOULS began as a series of simple colorful paintings that grew over time into an expansive collection of never before seen digital beings built with love and shaped between two friends. SOULS exist as virtual objects that can bounce, wiggle, dance, sleep, and even sing. Join the galaxy to see what we can create together!
